root ignore
Type: object

ignore patterns to skip interface, ip address or routing objects

 No Additional Properties

root ignore ipaddr_builtin
Type: array of string

list of ip address prefixes to be ignored

Each item of this array must be:

root ignore ipaddr_builtin ipaddr_builtin items
Type: string

ip address with prefix length
Example:

"fe80::/10"

root ignore ipaddr
Type: array of string

list of ip address prefixes to be ignored

Each item of this array must be:

root ignore ipaddr ipaddr items
Type: string

ip address with prefix length
Example:

"fe80::/10"

root ignore ipaddr_dynamic
Type: boolean Default: true

ignore dynamic assigned ip addresses

root ignore ifname_builtin
Type: array of string

interface names matching this list of regex will be ignored

Each item of this array must be:

root ignore ifname_builtin ifname_builtin items
Type: string

regex to match interface name
Examples:

"^br-[\\da-f]{12}"

"^docker\\d+"

"^lo$"

"^ppp\\d+$"

"^veth"

"^virbr\\d+"

"^vrrp\\d*\\.\\d+$"

root ignore ifname
Type: array of string

interface names matching this list of regex will be ignored

Each item of this array must be:

root ignore ifname ifname items
Type: string

regex to match interface name
Examples:

"^br-[\\da-f]{12}"

"^docker\\d+"

"^lo$"

"^ppp\\d+$"

"^veth"

"^virbr\\d+"

"^vrrp\\d*\\.\\d+$"

Type: array of string

"192.0.2.1"

"192.168.0.1/24"

"2001:db8::1/64"
